⍝ InnerProduct.tc
⍝ ═══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO and RO dyadic functions
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (¯1↓⍴A),1↓⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ,0⌈¯2+(⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (4 5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A +.× B
      (⍴Z) ≡ (¯1↓⍴A),1↓⍴B
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,0⌈¯2+(⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: Z[I;J] ←→ ⊂+/A[I;]×B[;J]
      Z[2;3] ≡ ⊂+/A[2;]×B[;3]
1
